    / Section - HTML to Haml
      
    %section.slide
      %h1 HTML to Haml
          
    %section.slide
      %h1 Won't Someone Think of the Designers?
      
    %section.slide
      %h1 (They're in the Audience - Say Hi!)
      
    %section.slide
      %h2 A Quick Note on the Examples
      %ul
        %li.slide <a href="http://sinatrarb.com">Sinatra</a> + <a href="http://imakewebthings.github.com/deck.js/">deck.js</a>
        %li.slide HTML output is generated by the Haml engine
